-- Edcon CEO Schrieber to Manage Edgars After Division Head Leaves
-- B y   F r a n z   W i l d
-- 2012-05-13T13:29:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-13/edcon-ceo-schrieber-to-manage-edgars-after-division-head-leaves.html
Jurgen Schreiber, chief executive
officer of Bain Capital LLC-controlled Edcon Holdings (Pty)
Ltd., will be responsible for its Edgars Department Stores after
Hugues Witvoet, the division’s head, left on May 9.  Edcon and Witvoet parted ways “by mutual agreement,”
Johannesburg-based Edcon Holdings said today in an e-mailed
statement. It didn’t give further details on Witvoet’s departure
saying it is a “confidential matter.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Franz Wild in Johannesburg at 
 fwild@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
